author: Jaxon Van Derbeken
title: Fears of failure grow for rods on Bay Bridge eastern span
text:
Photo: Justin Sullivan, Getty Images A view of the eastern span of the Bay Bridge on May 18, 2015. A view of the eastern span of the Bay Bridge on May 18, 2015.
New documents raise questions about the integrity of the steel rods that hold together the Bay Bridge eastern span and point to potentially widespread problems that experts warn could lead to premature failure.
